  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates that resiniferatoxin (RTX) has dual effects: it reduces bladder neuron excitability during cross-sensitization but increases somatic field responses, limiting its therapeutic potential.",
    "The experimental model uses TNBS-induced colitis to study colon-bladder cross-sensitization in rats.",
    "TRPV1 receptors play a key role in pelvic organ cross-sensitization and neurogenic inflammation."
